# ================= SPRING CONFIG (CRITICAL) =================
# Block the LOCAL properties file (has real secrets)
**/application.properties
**/application.yml
**/application-local.properties
**/application-local.yml

# ✅ ALLOW docker and prod profiles — they only use ${ENV_VAR} placeholders
!**/application-docker.properties
!**/application-prod.properties

